All Classes

Class Description
Carte
Represents a card in the game
Compteur
The Compteur is an agent whose role will be to find the scores of the different players at the end of a round.
ControleurVueGraphique
This class is the controller of our program.
Couleur
Represents the different colors of a card.
Forme
Represents the different geometries of a card.
Joueur
This abstract class will be used for representing a player of the game.
JoueurReel
This class represents a real player.
JoueurVirtuel
This class represents a virtual player: the AI
Partie  
Plateau
This abstract class will be used to implement the boards of the game The game will offer two boards : a rectangular and a square board.
PlateauCarre
Represents a board that is going to look like a square at the end of a game round.
PlateauGraphique
This class represents the graphical board.
PlateauRectangulaire
Represents a board that is going to look like a rectangle at the end of a game round.
PosiCarte
Is used as an argument transmitted to the graphical view so that it can display the cards on the board
Remplissage
Represents the fact that a card is filled or not.
StadePartie
Gives the state of the game Either the state is neutral (Neutre) , either the game is waiting for a player to play (Movement), either it is the time to give the scores (Score)
Strategie
This interface gives the ability to virtual players to implement a game strategy It is a step in using the Strategy design pattern
StrategieVAdvancedRandom
This class represents the strategy used in the Advanced ShapeUp scenario
StrategieVClassique
This class represents the normal strategy used in the normal ShapeUp scenario
StrategieVClassiqueRandom
This class represents the random strategy used in the normal ShapeUp scenario
Variante
Defines an interface for the game scenarios.
VarianteAdvanced
This class represents the advanced ShapeUp game scenario.
VarianteClassique
This class represents the normal ShapeUp game scenario.
VisiteurPlateau
This interface implies the ability to visit a board in the context of the design pattern Visitor.
VueConsole
This class represents the console.
VueGraphique
This class represents the whole graphical user interface.
ZoneDeJeu
This class represents the whole space where the players play.
ZoneJoueur
This class represents the hand of a player.
